      <td width="573">
  <p align="center">This is the third of the earring quests. You must have 
  completed the second quest to do this part.</p>

  <hr noshade>

      </div>

  <p align="left">Talk to Tilbok Furrunner who can be found on the third floor 
  of the castle&nbsp; in Katta Castellum. Hand him the report from Euzan Jurek, 
  and you'll receive a small satchel in return. </p>
  <p align="left">He asks you to collect reports from each of the Consilliums. 
  To do this you must kill a Lictor of the Heart, A Vigilum Cohortis, A 
  Signiferi of the Hand, and A Custos Armorum. They do not drop the report every 
  time and you will need a solid group or possibly more depending on your 
  strength to take them.</p>
  <p align="left">&nbsp;Combine these reports and give them along with your 
  etched earring back to Tibok to recieve the Runed Earring of Veracity.<font color="white" size="2" face="Microsoft Sans Serif"><br>
&nbsp;</font></p>

